      %section.container.info_title#apply
        .vertical_line
          .circle_bottom
        %i.fa.fa-check-circle-o.right
        .row.wow.info_vertical.animated.fadeInUp
          %h1 Apply to Join!
        .row.wow.info_vertical.animated.fadeInUp.padding_bottom
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-6.col-lg-6.text-left
            %h3 Application Process
            %p 
              Complete each of the onboading tasks to gain access to our private mailing list, monthly meetings, and our
              %a{:href=>"https://github.com/orgs/openshift-evangelists/teams/accelerators", :title=>"OpenShift Accelerators Team on GitHub"}
              OpenShift Accelerators Team on GitHub.
            %br/
            %p 
              Active team members may be eligible for material support (event sponsorship, training promotions, free stickers, etc)
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-6.col-lg-6.text-left
            %h3
              How to get started
            %ol
              %li
                Watch the 
                %a{:href=>"https://github.com/openshift/origin-server", :title=>"OpenShift project on GitHub"} OpenShift project on GitHub
              %li
                Join the 
                %a{ :href=>"https://plus.google.com/u/0/communities/114361859072744017486", :title=>"OpenShift G+ community as a member"} OpenShift Community on G+
              %li
                Take some time and explore 
                %a{ :href=>"https://www.openshift.com/walkthrough/how-it-works", :title=>"OpenShift"} OpenShift
            %p 
              Then, apply to become a member of the OpenShift Accelerators program:
            %br/
            %p.text-center
              %a{:href=>"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1q4IBEXvg8ZharjovlsY7jjjhSjDkq6UzorYV23_vpSg/viewform", :title=>"Join the OpenShift Accelerators"}
